{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Block (CSS)","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Block/CSS","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>网页上的区块指的是出现在新行上的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Element\">元素</a>，即在该元素的前一个元素的下方，在后一个元素之上（通常称为块级元素）。例如，HTML 中的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> 元素默认是<em>块级元素</em>，而 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a> 元素是一个<em>内联元素</em> - 你可以在 HTML 源码中将多个标记紧挨着写在一起，渲染结果是，它们将在同一行显示。</p>\n<p>通过使用 CSS 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/display\"><code>display</code></a> 属性，你可以更改元素是内联还是块（在许多其他选项中）; <strong>块</strong>也受到定位方案（positioning schemes）和使用 CSS 中 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/position\"><code>position</code></a> 属性的影响。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"Learn more","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"General knowledge","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model\">Visual formatting model</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Learn more","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"网页上的区块指的是出现在新行上的 HTML 元素，即在该元素的前一个元素的下方，在后一个元素之上（通常称为块级元素）。例如，HTML 中的 <p> 元素默认是块级元素，而 <a> 元素是一个内联元素 - 你可以在 HTML 源码中将多个标记紧挨着写在一起，渲染结果是，它们将在同一行显示。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Block (CSS)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Block (CSS)","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Block (CSS)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Block (ブロック) (CSS)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"블록 (CSS)","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Bloco (block) - CSS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Блок (CSS)","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"區塊 (CSS)","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh